    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for your next adventure? This well-maintained vehicle is in good condition and has been cared for with pride. It runs smoothly, looks great, and is ready to provide many more miles of reliable driving. If you're looking for a solid, dependable car that\u2019s ready to go today, this is the one for you!",
