      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the most exacting standards. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Mechanically superior and cosmetically pristine, this vehicle has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our criteria for absolute excellence. A definitive choice for the discerning collector or professional.",
      "price": 46500.0,
